Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.07,0:19:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,有话好说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.29,0:19:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.29,0:19:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,灵幻先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.93,0:19:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,及时赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.60,0:20:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,社长,这次我也试着鼓起勇气了
